---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="Strategic Foundation" section="foundation">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">01 · Strategic Foundation</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Strategic priorities, <em>the revenue model.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">Captured from the final-round conversation. The strategic anchors for everything else in this hub.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="foundation"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="foundation">0 / 0</span> validated</p>

  <h2>Jim's stated priorities</h2>
  <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:65ch">Validate each in your first 1:1 conversations. Mark when you've confirmed shared understanding.</p>

  <div data-section="foundation">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-01-messaging" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Messaging shift: "Take your practice back" — 45 → 15 min demo</div><div class="task-meta">Outcome-led, not feature-led. Replace vendor demo language across all touchpoints.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-02-website" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Website rebuild — embody customer outcome positioning</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-03-ai-first" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">AI-first operations — scale via workflows, not headcount</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-04-member-outreach" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Fix member outreach — one renewal email/year is top operational gap</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-05-partnerships" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Extend partnerships beyond press releases — co-marketing, joint webinars</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-06-tiktok" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Test TikTok / influencer content — dentists, hygienists, front office, possibly gamified</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-07-aeo" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">AEO accuracy refresh — info across AI assistants is outdated, references Kleer/Membersy</div><div class="task-meta">top strategic concern. Q1 priority.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-08-directory" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Patient directory — Jim loved the concept</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-09-employer" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Employer channel — SMB businesses without insurance offering memberships</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="foundation-10-payment" data-section="foundation" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Payment plan partnership in progress — bridges $4-5K procedures</div><div class="task-meta">Sunbit is the verified best fit (1.9% practice fee, 0-14.99% APR)</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <h2>The revenue model <em>shapes everything.</em></h2>
  <p>Clerri's economics are tied to enrollment volume at member practices. Every additional patient enrolled at an existing practice is direct recurring revenue. Unusual for B2B SaaS — changes how marketing prioritizes investment.</p>

  <div class="grid-3">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.15em">BUCKET 01</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">New Logo</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem">Practices and DSOs signing onto the platform. Traditional B2B SaaS demand gen — paid, content, partnerships, ABM.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="background:var(--zest);border-color:var(--clerri-green)">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.15em">BUCKET 02 · LIKELY HIGHEST ROI</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Expansion</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem">Driving enrollment velocity at existing practices. Given practice density + the one-email-per-year problem, this is likely the highest-ROI motion at Clerri.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.15em">BUCKET 03</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Retention</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem">Keeping practices AND members. Customer marketing, lifecycle, NPS, advocacy. Compounds with Bucket 02.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Audience map</h2>
  <p>Multi-stakeholder by design. Each segment needs distinct messaging, content, and channels.</p>

  <div class="grid-3">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Buyers</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.9rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Independent practice owners (solo + small group)</li>
        <li>Group practice decision-makers (5-25 locations)</li>
        <li>DSO executives (CEO, CFO, CMO at 25+ locations)</li>
        <li>SMB employers (potential — employer channel)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Internal stakeholders</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.9rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Office managers / front desk (gatekeepers, often kill-switch)</li>
        <li>Hygienists and clinical staff (in-chair enrollment)</li>
        <li>Practice owner spouses/partners (financial decision shadow)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>End beneficiaries</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.9rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Uninsured adults (72M+, CareQuest 2024)</li>
        <li>Underinsured (insurance cap issues)</li>
        <li>Young adults aged out of parental coverage</li>
        <li>Senior post-employer coverage gap (Medicare)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">Strategic priorities — validation notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="foundation-jim-validation" placeholder="What the CEO said in your first 1:1, what shifted, what new priorities emerged, what got de-prioritized..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri"><span class="dir">← Back</span><span class="name">00 · Dashboard</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/market"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">02 · Market Context</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
